OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774436770
OL,3,CTaxpayer support: The cavalry is
OL,4,Ccoming but not for everyone
OL,6,FRachel Reeves says she is "contingency
OL,7,Fplanning" and points out, fairly, that
OL,8,Fthe economic impact of the war is
OL,9,Funcertain.
OL,11,FShe has also said any future support
OL,12,Fpackage would be constrained by her
OL,13,F"ironclad fiscal rules".
OL,15,FAs of last month, the chancellor had
OL,16,F#24 billion of headroom against her
OL,17,Fself-imposed rules, which limit how
OL,18,Fmuch she can borrow and spend.
OL,26,@nD@[OUoD@IO]uD@AOUuD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
