OL,3,CTaxpayer support: The cavalry is
OL,4,Ccoming but not for everyone
OL,6,FCapital Economics estimates that
OL,7,Fbuffer has been almost halved, as the
OL,8,Fwar in the Gulf has pushed up energy
OL,9,Fprices and borrowing costs.
OL,11,FOne-off help would not affect the
OL,12,Ftargets the chancellor has to meet -
OL,13,Fwhich do not bite until 2029/30.
OL,15,FBut if she permanently scraps the
OL,16,Fplanned fuel duty rise from September,
OL,17,Fher cushion would shrink further.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
