OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774436770
OL,3,CTaxpayer support: The cavalry is
OL,4,Ccoming but not for everyone
OL,6,FPaul Dales, Chief UK economist at
OL,7,FCapital Economics, believes the
OL,8,Fchancellor is right to target any
OL,9,Ffuture support, and argues the latest
OL,10,Fenergy price shock is smaller than the
OL,11,Flast.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,F"The oil price today is similar to
OL,19,F2022, but the key difference is that
OL,20,Fgas prices are much lower," says Dales.
OL,26,@zD@AOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
