CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1774436770
OL,3,CTaxpayer support: The cavalry is
OL,4,Ccoming but not for everyone
OL,6,FThe typical annual gas and electricity
OL,7,Fbill is expected to fall to #1,641
OL,8,Fnext month, before rising again by
OL,9,Faround #300 in July.
OL,11,FThat may not approach the extreme
OL,12,Flevels of four years ago, but it will
OL,13,Fstill hurt. And the chancellor has yet
OL,14,Fto say who she is prepared to help, or
OL,15,Fby how much.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
